cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper deals with the application of deep learning techniques to the analysis of MRI images for the diagnosis of hydrocephalus. This falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of transfer learning is also mentioned, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the study involves the analysis of medical images, which could also fall under the category of multimedia (cs.MM).
